Repository state handoff - 2026-05-12

Completed slice:
- Added Chumsky 0.13.0-based lexer foundation in `linguini-syntax`.
- Added token/span model and lexer tests for schema fixture, locale fixture, raw text, multiline text, placeholders, comments, doc comments, and byte spans.
- Added lexer recovery via `lex_with_recovery`, preserving strict `lex` behavior for callers that want the first error.
- Added committed snapshot-style lexer token fixtures for schema and locale golden files.
- Added schema parser AST and `parse_schema` entry point for enums, custom scalar aliases, schema formatter annotations, message signatures, grouped messages, and doc comments.
- Added schema-specific `lex_schema` so schema `type Name = Target @annotation` stays in code mode while locale `=` retains raw-text behavior.
- Updated parser checklist items for the completed schema slice.

Implementation decisions:
- Lexer uses `chumsky = "0.13.0"`.
- Public spans are byte offsets.
- Raw text after `=` and `=>` currently includes leading spaces, matching "text after delimiter" literally.
- `lex_schema` disables raw-text transition after `=` because schema custom scalar aliases use code syntax after equals.
- Mode transitions are coordinated in Rust, while token recognition is done with Chumsky parsers.
- `TokenKind::Error` represents recovered invalid source characters.
- Placeholder mode tokenizes code punctuation without letting `=` switch into raw text.
- Multiline raw text currently treats `"` as a delimiter boundary so triple quotes can be recognized; escaped/ordinary quotes in raw text are deferred.
- Parser trivia stripping removes whitespace, newlines, and ordinary comments, but preserves doc comments as AST nodes.
- Schema parser is syntax-only and does not resolve type names or formatter semantics.

Tests last run:
- `cargo test -p linguini-syntax`
- `cargo fmt --all --check`
- `./scripts/check-file-size.sh` (warned that `crates/linguini-syntax/src/lexer.rs` has 422 lines; below 500-line failure threshold)
- `cargo clippy --workspace --all-targets -- -D warnings`
- `cargo test --workspace`

Known deferred work:
- Locale parser implementation has not started.
- Parser recovery is not implemented yet.
- Raw text quote handling should be revisited when parser fixtures cover quoted localized text.

Next recommended task:
- Implement the locale parser for message implementations, placeholders, forms, selector maps, plural-map-shaped branches, and local functions.
